product.longDescription: Smooth, 6–8 oz. pink beefsteak with lightly ribbed shoulders. Exceptional flavor, aroma, and texture. A strong disease resistance package keeps the plants healthy. Tidy clusters set fruit consistently up the vine for a sustained harvest and high yield potential. High resistance to Fusarium crown and root rot, Fusarium wilt races 1 and 2, leaf mold, tomato apex necrosis virus, tomato mosaic virus, and Verticillium wilt; and intermediate resistance to gray leaf spot. Indeterminate. USDA Certified Organic. Avg. 194,700 seeds/lb. Packet: 15 seeds.
